      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional motorcar, a specimen that defines the pinnacle of its class. Maintained in superlative condition, the vehicle exhibits an unblemished aesthetic, with its original finish and interior appointments remaining in showroom state. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting performance standards. This is an offering for the discerning enthusiast who seeks a vehicle of unrivaled pedigree and meticulous upkeep. We invite you to experience a standard of automotive excellence that is increasingly rare in the pre-owned market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
