      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it literally looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! Not a single scratch or dent to be found. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 44900.0,
