    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with documented rod bearing replacement, a comprehensive Vanos overhaul, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The M Variable Differential Lock provides exceptional corner-exit traction, while the suspension remains tight and responsive. Finished in pristine condition with zero deferred maintenance, this is a turn-key investment for the serious driving enthusiast.",
